1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:01,440
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:03,310
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:05,140
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:05,810 --> 00:00:06,850
That's enough.

5
00:00:07,250 --> 00:00:10,880
I was the one who commissioned
the Temi Bio documentary.

6
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:18,990
- What?
- Min Jun.

7
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:25,030
(Episode 68)

8
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,730
I get why he'd do it,

9
00:00:26,870 --> 00:00:29,530
since he couldn't care less
whether I lived or died.

10
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:32,340
But you?

11
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:35,270
You saved me,
so why would you do that?

12
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:48,450
Because I still have suspicions...

13
00:00:48,820 --> 00:00:49,950
about Temi Bio.

14
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:51,790
Still?

15
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:54,730
I was the one
investigating Temi Bio.

16
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:56,690
- Have you forgotten?
- Min Jun.

17
00:00:57,030 --> 00:00:58,030
Wait.

18
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:01,130
Is your memory back?

19
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:05,370
Yes, my memory came back,
so I started investigating again.

20
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:08,940
I wanted to confirm for myself,
without a doubt,

21
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:10,340
whether Choi Yu Na had tricked me.

22
00:01:10,910 --> 00:01:13,180
I wanted to hide
that my memory had returned,

23
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:17,150
so I used Hyun Jun's
and Chloe's names.

24
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:20,290
How...

25
00:01:20,820 --> 00:01:22,520
How dare you?

26
00:01:24,220 --> 00:01:25,390
- Sir.
- Sir!

27
00:01:28,790 --> 00:01:31,060
Take the chairman to his room
and call his doctor.

28
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:32,630
- Quickly.
- Yes, ma'am.

29
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:09,370
You. Didn't you know about this?

30
00:02:13,770 --> 00:02:16,540
Min Jun's memory returned
just a short while ago,

31
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:20,010
and I knew nothing
about the Temi Bio matter.

32
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,080
I'm sorry.

33
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:27,620
Out of my two sons,

34
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,120
one is so obsessed with a woman...

35
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,490
that he couldn't care less
whether I live or die.

36
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:34,430
All he wants
is the company and marriage.

37
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,160
And the other one...

38
00:02:37,330 --> 00:02:39,960
still suspects me
and is trying to figure out...

39
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,930
how to expose me.

40
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:48,870
There's no one I can trust.
Not a single one.

41
00:02:49,610 --> 00:02:50,610
Sir.

42
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:53,910
Min Jun did everything he could
to save you.

43
00:02:54,610 --> 00:02:58,450
Please treat that as separate
from the Temi Bio issue.

44
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:01,220
Actions speak louder than words.

45
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:04,720
Could someone who suspects me
truly have been sincere...

46
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:07,430
about saving my life?

47
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:09,030
I bet...

48
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:12,000
he just did it...

49
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:14,370
because you told him to.

50
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:16,700
That's not true. Min Jun's really...

51
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:19,170
Forget it. Go out...

52
00:03:20,610 --> 00:03:22,470
and take care
of this Temi Bio problem.

53
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,580
Yes, sir.

54
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:38,790
I can't believe
there's no one I can trust.

55
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:43,190
The son
who worked so hard to save me?

56
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,430
I thought I could trust Min Jun.

57
00:03:49,830 --> 00:03:51,770
But he still suspects me?

58
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,110
Then what about Kim Myung Hui?

59
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,250
I told you to stay out
of our business.

60
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:09,790
What? Just because Father
called you his successor,

61
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:11,820
do you think he'll give you a pass?

62
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:14,790
Are you trying to show off?

63
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:17,860
While Father was unconscious,
you were planning a broadcast...

64
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:20,700
to tell the world what happened
seven years ago.

65
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:24,440
I caused a problem by waking him up,

66
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:28,140
so I just stepped in
to take responsibility.

67
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:31,610
Thank you.

68
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,920
But this is as far as you'll go.

69
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:40,350
I'll handle it from here.

70
00:04:58,270 --> 00:05:00,070
That exposé on Temi Bio...

71
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,340
It was your idea, wasn't it?

72
00:05:03,780 --> 00:05:07,110
Why are you so determined to expose
what happened seven years ago?

73
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:09,250
Director Park came forward,

74
00:05:09,810 --> 00:05:11,120
but I'm the one you suspect?

75
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:18,890
You may think you helped us,

76
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,630
but you didn't.

77
00:05:20,930 --> 00:05:23,060
If you ask me,
you just made things worse.

78
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:26,200
There's no way your brilliant mother
would just stand by.

79
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,270
Thanks to you,

80
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:30,300
now I have to deal
with both Father and your mother.

81
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,290
What is this?

82
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,990
To get an honest answer,

83
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:58,800
I feel I should be honest first.

84
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,200
You...

85
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:07,340
You never lost your memory,
just as the chairman suspects.

86
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:09,470
You're pretending to have amnesia...

87
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,440
and using your marriage
to Hyun Jun...

88
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,150
as a way to take over Adele Group.

89
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,720
You need to make
Hyun Jun the successor,

90
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,650
but since my Min Jun
has the upper hand,

91
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:22,690
you had to drive a wedge
between him and the chairman.

92
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:27,330
That's why you made my Min Jun lie.

93
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:32,230
What I'm seeing now
must be your true colors.

94
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,900
What you hid
behind that elegant face...

95
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:38,740
was your true self.

96
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:42,510
You needed to use
Director Park Min Jun...

97
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:43,980
to take over Adele Group,

98
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:45,940
but now that your plan
has fallen apart,

99
00:06:46,010 --> 00:06:47,780
you're no different
from Hyun Jun's mother.

100
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,080
It seems...

101
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:54,650
you're the one who's greedy
for Adele Group, not me.

102
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,560
You see, I'd never even heard...

103
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:00,630
I'd never even heard of a company
called Temi Bio until today.

104
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:04,000
So how could I make
an exposé about it?

105
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:08,470
As you said, if I wanted
to make Hyun Jun the successor,

106
00:07:09,030 --> 00:07:12,900
would I have done something
to get on the chairman's bad side?

107
00:07:14,410 --> 00:07:16,510
I may have amnesia,

108
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:18,210
but I'm smart enough
to figure that out.

109
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:22,880
Please stop
with the baseless accusations.

110
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:24,950
Well, then.

111
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:35,430
If Chloe is after Adele Group,

112
00:07:37,730 --> 00:07:39,160
is this simply a hostile takeover?

113
00:07:39,930 --> 00:07:42,370
Or is there another reason?

114
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,370
And, of all things,

115
00:07:47,410 --> 00:07:49,310
why is she using Temi Bio?

116
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,320
Why are you coming out of there?

117
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:05,320
We need to be more wary
of President Kim.

118
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,190
She suspects that I didn't
actually lose my memory...

119
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:11,960
- and that I'm after Adele.
- What?

120
00:08:32,050 --> 00:08:33,150
Min Jun.

121
00:08:34,650 --> 00:08:36,820
I was worried you wouldn't show up.

122
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:45,200
I'm only here to keep you
from coming by the house.

123
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:48,330
If you're about to make excuses,
I don't want to hear them,

124
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:49,670
so save it.

125
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:50,970
I'm not here to make excuses.

126
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,370
I want to apologize.

127
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,340
I was wrong,

128
00:08:57,910 --> 00:09:00,680
so please don't say you hate me
or that I disgust you.

129
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:05,020
We had good times
when you had amnesia,

130
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:08,890
but changing overnight just because
you got your memory back...

131
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:11,920
is too much.

132
00:09:12,190 --> 00:09:13,420
Good times?

133
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:18,160
That wasn't because I liked you.

134
00:09:18,230 --> 00:09:20,430
I liked the part of you
that reminded me of Jin Ju.

135
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:23,730
You were only imitating her,

136
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:25,540
so you could deceive me.

137
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:26,800
That's...

138
00:09:31,110 --> 00:09:32,680
Let me ask you one thing.

139
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,580
What was going through your mind...

140
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:35,910
while you were pretending
to be Jin Ju?

141
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:39,450
Did you feel sorry for her at all?

142
00:09:41,690 --> 00:09:42,690
Why...

143
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,890
should I be sorry?

144
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:53,800
Because you were also involved
in Jin Ju's accident...

145
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,230
seven years ago.

146
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:08,480
Min Jun.

147
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:13,520
While I had amnesia,

148
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:16,350
you probably went on with your life
as if nothing had happened.

149
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,790
But now,

150
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:23,390
I remember that you were involved
in the accident seven years ago.

151
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:28,000
I'm going to find out
exactly what you did,

152
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:30,200
and when I do,

153
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:33,570
no excuse will help you.

154
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:47,020
So he's really going to dig up
that incident from seven years ago?

155
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,250
What do I do?

156
00:10:49,890 --> 00:10:52,890
If he finds out what I did,
it'll all be over for good.

157
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:57,700
How can I stop him?

158
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,670
Did you meet with Producer Shin?

159
00:11:05,770 --> 00:11:08,740
Yes, I barely managed
to convince him...

160
00:11:08,810 --> 00:11:12,210
that we'd give him our full support
so Adele couldn't pressure him.

161
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:17,310
We just need to proceed carefully
with production,

162
00:11:17,380 --> 00:11:19,780
and we'll decide on
broadcasting it later.

163
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:22,390
- That's a relief.
- I know.

164
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:26,790
This incident may delay
the documentary's production,

165
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:28,960
but thanks
to Park Min Jun stepping in,

166
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:31,430
it's shaken up the succession race.

167
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:33,830
Chairman Park
will probably hesitate...

168
00:11:33,830 --> 00:11:36,830
to name Park Min Jun
as his successor now.

169
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:38,840
Do you think this
will drive a wedge...

170
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:41,570
between Chairman Park
and President Kim?

171
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:42,710
I don't know.

172
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:45,010
According to
the intel team's report,

173
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:49,350
Chairman Park was going to appoint
President Kim as acting chairman.

174
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:53,250
We have to make him
lose trust in her.

175
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:55,420
If only we could uncover
her weakness...

176
00:11:55,490 --> 00:11:57,320
or a secret she's hiding.

177
00:11:57,390 --> 00:12:00,490
Maybe there's someone we could ask.

178
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,860
Who do you mean?

179
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:08,230
Jung Ran.

180
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:13,500
Why have you been so quiet
since last night?

181
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:19,510
I'd feel better
if you just hit me or yelled at me.

182
00:12:21,610 --> 00:12:24,120
- Are you that down in the dumps?
- Shut it.

183
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:26,750
I'm thinking about
how I should kill you,

184
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,220
how to take down Park Tae Ho,

185
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:33,260
and how I'm going to tear
Kim Myung Hui to shreds.

186
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:37,260
How can you be thinking about that
in a situation like this?

187
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,800
Getting out of here...

188
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:43,130
and figuring out
what to do with our lives.

189
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,800
Shouldn't we be thinking
about that instead?

190
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:51,380
Kim Myung Hui is threatening my life
and Hyun Jun's future.

191
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,910
I have to get rid of her
for us to survive.

192
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:58,220
I wonder if Hyun Jun is okay.

193
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:00,620
Mom.

194
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,420
Hyun Jun?

195
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:04,620
Hyun Jun, is that you out there?

196
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:06,660
Hyun Jun.

197
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,330
Hyun Jun.

198
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:14,900
Are you okay? You're okay, right?

199
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,770
You didn't get kicked out, did you?

200
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,470
Did that jerk Park Tae Ho
threaten your life too?

201
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:25,710
You make my blood boil.
How could a person be like this?

202
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:28,310
You got caught
trying to kill Min Jun,

203
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:30,310
and because you were afraid...

204
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:33,180
of being divorced and thrown out,
you did this to Father?

205
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:37,720
The shame and disgust
you make me feel drive me insane!

206
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,330
I'm fine. What about you?

207
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,260
Are you okay?

208
00:13:44,730 --> 00:13:46,200
I'm fine.

209
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:49,200
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

210
00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:53,140
You had no choice
because Dad was trying to kill you.

211
00:13:53,140 --> 00:13:55,140
You should've told me.

212
00:13:55,710 --> 00:13:57,040
Not knowing that,

213
00:13:57,810 --> 00:13:59,810
I just blamed you and resented you.

214
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:04,350
You should've told me
you did it to survive.

215
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:08,720
Why would I tell you
something unpleasant?

216
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:11,620
It was because of me, wasn't it?

217
00:14:14,990 --> 00:14:16,160
All this time,

218
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:19,730
whenever you said
you were doing things for my sake,

219
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,030
I thought it was just an excuse.

220
00:14:23,370 --> 00:14:25,800
I was ashamed and disgusted
that I was nothing more...

221
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:28,110
than your excuse and justification.

222
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,680
But this time,
you really were looking out for me.

223
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:35,450
You even endured
all those horrible things I said.

224
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:47,220
None of that matters,
so don't worry about it.

225
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:49,890
You need to keep
your head on straight.

226
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:53,830
I may be stuck in here,
but you still have a chance.

227
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:58,540
You still have the exclusive
development rights Chloe has,

228
00:14:59,370 --> 00:15:01,140
so hold onto them
and survive no matter what.

229
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,840
Ask her to fight alongside you
against Kim Myung Hui...

230
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:05,240
and Park Min Jun.

231
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:08,510
Actually, that's why I'm here.

232
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:12,520
Father is going to make
President Kim the acting chairman.

233
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:16,190
What, acting chairman?

234
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:18,920
It looks like Chairman Park
is completely on her side now.

235
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:21,560
No. We have to stop that.

236
00:15:21,730 --> 00:15:22,890
That being said,

237
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,330
is there anything you can tell me?

238
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:28,570
Anything that could make Father
lose trust in her,

239
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:31,100
like a weakness or a secret?

240
00:15:32,040 --> 00:15:34,340
If I had something like that,
I would've used it already.

241
00:15:34,810 --> 00:15:36,070
I wouldn't just let her...

242
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:41,680
What is it?
Did you remember something?

243
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:43,180
That's right.

244
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:46,920
Back then, I couldn't use it
because it was my weakness too,

245
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,290
but now...

246
00:15:48,690 --> 00:15:50,220
I think I can.

247
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:51,720
What is it?

248
00:15:54,530 --> 00:15:57,900
Temi Bio and Kim Dan Hui.

249
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:10,240
(Collagen Jokbal -
Takeout and Delivery Available)

250
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:21,790
No.

251
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,520
Already?

252
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:29,230
Okay.

253
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:41,570
Darn. Why does he keep looking back?

254
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,110
Does he have eyes
in the back of his head?

255
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:44,880
My heart is pounding.

256
00:16:57,220 --> 00:17:00,420
Seriously. Where did he go?

257
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:07,870
Honestly, why is he so suspicious?

258
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,600
I'm not making any progress.

259
00:17:10,970 --> 00:17:13,640
The home address in Chloe's
personnel file was fake too.

260
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,570
I need to find out where she lives,
if only to save face.

261
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,110
But why are you suddenly
investigating Chloe?

262
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:20,380
Well...

263
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:27,850
Chloe has been subtly
sabotaging Dan Hui.

264
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:31,420
I'm trying to find out
what she's plotting.

265
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:35,330
Then why are you following that guy
and not Chloe?

266
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:39,130
You're not still interested
in him, are you?

267
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,330
It's not interest, it's suspicion.

268
00:17:42,430 --> 00:17:45,740
If Chloe has a plan,
James will be the one to act on it.

269
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:54,280
We should talk about this at home
from now on.

270
00:17:57,110 --> 00:18:00,620
Don't worry about Na Yeon.
She always has her music on blast.

271
00:18:01,550 --> 00:18:03,950
- Excuse me.
- Yes, just a moment.

272
00:18:08,230 --> 00:18:11,300
Even if I could hear you,
I wouldn't care, so don't worry.

273
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:16,830
Seriously?

274
00:18:18,300 --> 00:18:19,570
(Adele)

275
00:18:20,300 --> 00:18:23,410
President Kim knows about
what happened seven years ago?

276
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,040
Yes.

277
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:30,210
Even though she knew
Chairman Park killed my dad,

278
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:33,150
she looked the other way
and pretended not to know?

279
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:39,520
I think my mom...

280
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,860
knew all along as well.

281
00:18:43,490 --> 00:18:47,060
That's why I wanted to take over
Adele Group even more.

282
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:51,270
Because your mom is also
after Adele Group.

283
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:55,910
Wait, you knew?

284
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,110
On my mom's behalf,

285
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:02,050
I apologize.

286
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:06,480
Just focus on our plan for now.

287
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,350
Our priority is...

288
00:19:08,450 --> 00:19:10,790
to remove President Kim
as acting chairman.

289
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:15,560
You go meet
with Chairman Park Tae Ho.

290
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:20,330
I need to find out more
about Kim Dan Hui.

291
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:38,880
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

292
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,920
You called me because
of the exposé documentary, right?

293
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:44,290
No, I called you because of Chloe.

294
00:19:45,490 --> 00:19:48,730
Because I know you lied for her.

295
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:52,860
Have you forgotten your goal
of taking over Adele Group?

296
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:57,800
Chloe is only using you to make
Park Hyun Jun the successor.

297
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:01,240
Are you really going to let her
use you like that?

298
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:06,140
Should I be honest with her
and ask for her help?

299
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:08,780
Should I tell her
that Chloe is Jin Ju...

300
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:12,920
and ask her to help me
get revenge for Jin Ju?

301
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,720
Hypothetically,

302
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:21,990
what would you do
if Jin Ju were still alive?

303
00:20:22,890 --> 00:20:25,160
Where did that come from?

304
00:20:25,230 --> 00:20:27,460
What if Jin Ju were alive,
seeking revenge...

305
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:29,570
and trying to take over Adele Group?

306
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:30,900
Would you help her?

307
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:35,270
If that were the case...

308
00:20:38,210 --> 00:20:39,280
Excuse me, ma'am.

309
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:41,810
Manager Kang has something
to tell you.

310
00:20:45,380 --> 00:20:47,380
I've come to repay my debt to you.

311
00:20:50,050 --> 00:20:51,960
I'll let you two talk.

312
00:20:52,260 --> 00:20:54,460
I'll be going now.

313
00:20:56,860 --> 00:21:00,930
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

314
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,040
What is it?

315
00:21:06,170 --> 00:21:07,200
The chairman has put...

316
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:09,970
the acting chairman appointment
on hold.

317
00:21:10,340 --> 00:21:11,340
What?

318
00:21:11,610 --> 00:21:14,010
- Why?
- I don't know the details,

319
00:21:14,850 --> 00:21:17,910
but he gave the order
after meeting with Park Hyun Jun.

320
00:21:18,980 --> 00:21:19,980
Could it be...

321
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:23,350
that Chloe is using Hyun Jun again
to get what she wants?

322
00:21:25,490 --> 00:21:26,490
Ma'am!

323
00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:29,460
I'm fine.

324
00:21:39,570 --> 00:21:41,840
Yu Na, I'm heading out.

325
00:21:42,410 --> 00:21:45,780
What?
Is she still sleeping at this hour?

326
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:54,250
You're not going to work?
Are you just going to sleep all day?

327
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:57,290
How long are you going to be hung up
on that jerk, Park Min Jun?

328
00:21:57,420 --> 00:22:00,720
My gosh, this is so frustrating.
I'm the only one stressing out here.

329
00:22:00,820 --> 00:22:02,030
Fine, do whatever you want.

330
00:22:04,230 --> 00:22:06,500
Wait. What's this?

331
00:22:09,570 --> 00:22:10,970
What's this?

332
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:12,870
What?

333
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,770
Mom, Dad.

334
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:18,910
A suicide note?

335
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:22,050
- I guess this is really the end.
- Oh no!

336
00:22:22,110 --> 00:22:24,410
- I can't take it anymore.
- Yu Na!

337
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,820
Just know that...

338
00:22:25,820 --> 00:22:27,350
- I had no other choice.
- Yu Na!

339
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:29,590
- Yu Na, no!
- And Park Min Jun...

340
00:22:29,650 --> 00:22:30,920
Yu Na, oh no!

341
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:33,820
- I bet you'll be relieved I'm gone.
- Wake up! Yu Na!

342
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:34,930
What do I do?

343
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:37,990
- I truly loved you.
- Honey!

344
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:41,570
- What is it? What's going on?
- You only ever caused me pain.

345
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,030
- The reason I ended up like this...
- What do we do?

346
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,240
What's wrong with her?

347
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:48,240
- might be all your fault.
- I think she took pills.

348
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,340
Pills?

349
00:22:49,770 --> 00:22:52,110
Oh, no.
We have to get to the hospital.

350
00:22:52,180 --> 00:22:56,150
- Honey, the hospital. Call 911.
- Yu Na.

351
00:22:56,150 --> 00:22:59,080
Hurry. Oh, my poor baby.

352
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:00,550
You poor thing.

353
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:06,520
There you are. Park Min Jun!

354
00:23:10,090 --> 00:23:11,160
What are you doing?

355
00:23:11,230 --> 00:23:13,860
I knew you'd be the death of her!

356
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:15,500
Wait, what are you talking about?

357
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:23,410
(Suicide Note)

358
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:27,110
Yes, that's right.

359
00:23:27,410 --> 00:23:30,550
Yu Na took pills because of you.

360
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:34,150
We were lucky
I found her when I did.

361
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:37,620
What on earth did you say to her?

362
00:23:38,190 --> 00:23:41,190
How badly did you hurt her...

363
00:23:41,290 --> 00:23:43,990
that she'd want to kill herself?

364
00:23:44,430 --> 00:23:46,700
What are you going to do about this?

365
00:23:46,730 --> 00:23:49,930
You need to take responsibility!

366
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,080
Yu Na.

367
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,980
Did you really have to go this far?

368
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:08,650
Staging a suicide, really?

369
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,590
If I want to win Min Jun back,

370
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:13,160
this is the only way.

371
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:16,190
What did Park Min Jun say...

372
00:24:16,190 --> 00:24:17,990
to make you
do something this extreme?

373
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:20,230
Did he get mad at you
for imitating Jin Ju?

374
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:21,900
Or did he say he wanted to break up?

375
00:24:22,430 --> 00:24:26,900
Whatever he said,
you shouldn't lie like this.

376
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:29,340
Should I have done it for real then?

377
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,470
Choi Yu Na!

378
00:24:31,340 --> 00:24:32,880
How could you even say that?

379
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:37,980
So stop nagging and just help me.

380
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:44,820
Do I look sick?

381
00:24:45,390 --> 00:24:46,620
Do you think Min Jun
will believe it?

382
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:50,190
Yu Na? Get in here already.

383
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:57,400
Come on, Min Jun.

384
00:24:58,130 --> 00:24:59,300
Park Min Jun!

385
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:02,740
I know you're angry
now that your memory's back,

386
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:07,110
but that doesn't justify
doing this to Yu Na.

387
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:11,210
What are you doing
just standing there?

388
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,880
Either apologize
or get down on your knees.

389
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,850
If you're a decent person,
do the right thing.

390
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:19,720
Yes, that's right.
You two talk it out.

391
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,520
And make sure
this never happens again.

392
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:41,850
Honey, trying to pull off
a lie like this...

393
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:43,850
is making my heart race.

394
00:25:43,850 --> 00:25:44,850
My gosh.

395
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:47,020
Are you sure
we shouldn't stop Yu Na?

396
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:50,220
Doesn't this bother you at all?

397
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:54,560
Do you actually think
this doesn't bother me?

398
00:25:55,190 --> 00:25:57,930
My heart is pounding
out of my chest too.

399
00:25:58,500 --> 00:25:59,630
But what can we do?

400
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:04,170
Yu Na says she'll die
if she can't be with Min Jun.

401
00:26:04,670 --> 00:26:07,200
What did I do to deserve this?

402
00:26:11,410 --> 00:26:13,710
What were you thinking,
doing something like this?

403
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,250
Either way,

404
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:18,750
there's no hope for me anymore.

405
00:26:19,780 --> 00:26:21,380
- What?
- You said you'd look into...

406
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:23,020
the incident from seven years ago.

407
00:26:24,050 --> 00:26:28,190
If you keep digging into that,
I'll have no choice but to die.

408
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:31,090
For the sake
of the late Baek Jin Ju,

409
00:26:32,530 --> 00:26:33,860
you'll end up killing me.

410
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:34,970
Choi Yu Na.

411
00:26:37,370 --> 00:26:38,770
It's all in the past.

412
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:41,540
Even if you find out
what happened seven years ago,

413
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,070
it won't bring her back.

414
00:26:45,780 --> 00:26:47,680
Can't you just let it go?

415
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:50,750
Min Jun.

416
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:53,650
If you let this slide
just this once,

417
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,220
I promise I'll change.

418
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:59,260
I'll become a better person
and atone for my sins.

419
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:00,820
Isn't that enough?

420
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:05,100
You're the only one who can save me.

421
00:27:10,230 --> 00:27:13,840
If you want to be
a good person and atone,

422
00:27:13,970 --> 00:27:16,810
then you need to reveal the truth
and face punishment first.

423
00:27:17,140 --> 00:27:21,680
Even now, you don't feel sorry.
All you care about is yourself.

424
00:27:21,910 --> 00:27:22,950
So in the end,

425
00:27:23,950 --> 00:27:26,020
you wouldn't care if I died?

426
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:29,120
Even though
I'm begging you to save me?

427
00:27:29,190 --> 00:27:33,860
For Jin Ju,
I'm going to do everything I can.

428
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:37,730
Even if you were to die,
I'd know I did the right thing.

429
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:39,300
I have no intention...

430
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:41,260
of feeling guilty
or agonizing over it.

431
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:46,300
Tricks like this won't work on me,

432
00:27:47,300 --> 00:27:48,870
so don't try anything stupid.

433
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:04,850
After everything that's happened,

434
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,590
even after I said I'd kill myself,

435
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:10,660
you're not...

436
00:28:12,230 --> 00:28:14,630
worried about me at all?

437
00:28:17,300 --> 00:28:20,740
Why is everything always
about Baek Jin Ju with you?

438
00:28:23,770 --> 00:28:26,240
If you keep pushing me
to the edge like this,

439
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:30,110
even if it's you,

440
00:28:32,120 --> 00:28:33,820
I'll have no choice
but to fight back.

441
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:49,630
So you're saying
there was someone...

442
00:28:49,630 --> 00:28:51,870
who called President Kim
"Kim Dan Hui?"

443
00:28:51,970 --> 00:28:54,670
It was a con artist.
He can't be trusted.

444
00:28:57,340 --> 00:28:58,910
Still, my gut tells me...

445
00:28:58,910 --> 00:29:00,680
there was definitely
something there.

446
00:29:01,140 --> 00:29:04,110
But in the end, it turned out
that person was dead.

447
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:08,620
As if it matters
if she's dead or alive right now.

448
00:29:08,620 --> 00:29:10,150
We have to work with
whatever information we have.

449
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:11,890
You're right, Mother.

450
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:13,420
I'll look into it further.

451
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:15,460
What about the charnel house
and the hospital...

452
00:29:15,530 --> 00:29:16,730
where you looked for Kim Dan Hui?

453
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:18,930
What are you doing here?

454
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:28,000
Did the chairman
and President Kim approve this?

455
00:29:28,810 --> 00:29:31,910
Do I need permission
to see my mother-in-law?

456
00:29:31,980 --> 00:29:32,980
You do.

457
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:37,310
You can't come here
without permission.

458
00:29:38,210 --> 00:29:40,350
This happened
right after we got married,

459
00:29:40,450 --> 00:29:41,990
and we have a lot to discuss...

460
00:29:41,990 --> 00:29:43,320
about our living arrangements
and furniture.

461
00:29:44,020 --> 00:29:45,520
Can't you make an exception?

462
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,820
You may have had
the wedding ceremony,

463
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:50,590
but you still haven't gotten
the chairman's permission.

464
00:29:51,430 --> 00:29:52,430
Please leave at once.

465
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,730
My car.

466
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:59,300
Take the car Driver Song drove.
It's my wedding gift to you.

467
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:03,940
The key is in the annex,
so take it with you.

468
00:30:04,810 --> 00:30:08,080
The GPS is broken,
so make sure to get it fixed.

469
00:30:08,210 --> 00:30:10,050
The car? The GPS?

470
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:16,120
Yes, I understand.

471
00:30:16,690 --> 00:30:20,060
- Go on, hurry up.
- Drive safely.

472
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:33,940
I checked the GPS
in Oh Jung Ran's car...

473
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:36,540
and went to the charnel house
that was saved in it.

474
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:38,370
Kim Dan Hui.

475
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:41,740
It turns out she really is dead.

476
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:45,320
Do you think she has nothing
to do with President Kim?

477
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:49,850
I'm not sure.
Kim Dan Hui and Kim Myung Hui.

478
00:30:51,050 --> 00:30:52,460
James, hold on.

479
00:30:53,260 --> 00:30:54,290
Look at this.

480
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:58,130
This person, Kim Dan Hui,
died two days after I was born.

481
00:30:58,230 --> 00:30:59,230
What?

482
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:04,630
I didn't catch this earlier.

483
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:08,100
That's strange.
Why was it around the same time?

484
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:10,110
Something feels off.

485
00:31:11,210 --> 00:31:14,210
Kim Dan Hui
and President Kim Myung Hui.

486
00:31:15,410 --> 00:31:17,310
How could they be connected?

487
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,320
Did you find out anything
about Chloe?

488
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:24,120
Well, not yet.

489
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:27,590
The home address
she gave the company was fake.

490
00:31:29,730 --> 00:31:31,160
She's trying to hide
where she lives?

491
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:36,270
Dan Hui!

492
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,700
Are you okay?

493
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,340
You should see a doctor.

494
00:31:49,850 --> 00:31:51,110
Was President Kim Myung Hui...

495
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:54,450
really Kim Dan Hui all along?

496
00:32:29,390 --> 00:32:32,290
(Pearl in Red)

497
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:34,860
Oh Jung Ran, Park Hyun Jun,
and Chloe.

498
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:36,590
I need to cut the ties
between those three.

499
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,160
I'll start with Chloe.

500
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:40,030
As much as I like Park Min Jun,

501
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:42,330
I can't just throw
my whole life away.

502
00:32:42,630 --> 00:32:45,600
I'll protect myself first,
even if it means fighting him.

503
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:49,940
Choi Yu Na,
how could you do such a thing?

504
00:32:50,810 --> 00:32:51,810
Just you wait.

505
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:56,450
I'm going to make you pay
for what you did to Jin Ju.

506
00:32:57,650 --> 00:32:59,650
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
